                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d592">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Governor Sir <persName type="from">W. MacGregor</persName> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Earl of Elgin</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1906-08-16T23:59:59+00:00"
                            notBefore="1906-08-14T00:00:00+00:00">undated</date>] (Received August
                        16, 1906.)</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 10.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>Have received from my ministers a comprehensive reply to your telegram and Mr.
                    Root’s communication. I shall forward copy by earliest opportunity. Next mail
                    leaves here Wednesday next.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
